Package: OPCC
Title: Open Postal Code Correspondence
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Lennon", "Li", email = "yeli@biostats.ai", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides source-qualified, reproducible many-to-many
    correspondence between Ontario postal codes and Statistics Canada 2021
    census geographies. Lookup results retain allocation weights, evidence
    source, lineage, method, and vintage; unmatched postal codes remain
    explicit. Versioned release artifacts are checksum-verified before use.
    The package does not redistribute Canada Post, 'PCCF', or 'PCCF+' data and
    does not claim authoritative postal assignments.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
URL: https://github.com/lennon-li/OPCC
BugReports: https://github.com/lennon-li/OPCC/issues
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: digest, jsonlite
